{"article_id":"IgOFuwXPr5JsfsUF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN ) -","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"In the wake of last week 's Supreme Court decision on President Barack Obama 's health care law ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"a senior adviser to Mitt Romney 's presidential campaign parted with Republican talking points Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"arguing","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"the mandate","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"that most individuals obtain health coverage","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"or pay a government fine","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"is `` not a tax . ''","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"The high court on Thursday found the individual unconstitutional under Congress ' ability","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to regulate commerce ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"but constitutional under Congress ' taxation power , language","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Republicans seized on in criticism of the law .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Since the ruling , Democrats have maintained","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that it is not a tax , but a penalty .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"- Check out the CNN Electoral Map and Calculator","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and game out your own strategy for November .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Eric Fehrnstrom , in an interview on MSNBC , said","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Romney agrees with President Obama","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"that the individual mandate is no tax .","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"`` He agreed with the dissent","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"written by Justice Scalia","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"which very clearly stated","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"that the mandate was not a tax , ''","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"Fehrnstrom said .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"When pressed repeatedly","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"if Romney agrees with Obama and Democrats","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"that the penalty is no tax ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"Fehrnstrom eventually said ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"`` That 's correct . ''","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Fehrnstrom came to national attention earlier this year during the Republican primaries","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"when he referred to the eventual switch to a general election campaign as being like an Etch-A-Sketch","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"where you can shake it","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"and start over .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"The remark created a firestorm","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"as Romney 's Republican primary opponents pointed to it","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"that he would not stand firm in his conservative policy positions","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"if he won the nomination .","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"Many Republicans , however , disagree with Fehrnstrom on `` tax '' versus `` penalty . '' `` This is a middle-class tax increase , ''","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Sen. Marco Rubio of Florida told CNN 's Candy Crowley hours after the decision .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"`` And you know why we know","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"it 's a middle class tax increase ?","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"Not because I 'm saying it ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"because the Supreme Court has said .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"It 's the basis","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"for them upholding it .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Americans now understand what this law really is all about . ''","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"House Budget Committee chairman Paul Ryan also called it a tax ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"and criticized the logic behind the court 's majority opinion .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"`` I agree with the dissenting judges .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"they basically had to rewrite the statute","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"in order to call this a tax , ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Ryan said Sunday on ABC News ' `` This Week . ''","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Previously , Romney has defended the law","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"he signed","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"when governor of Massachusetts ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"called by some Romneycare ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"which included a similar individual mandate on a state level .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"While Republicans have been vocal about pointing to the penalty","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"being termed a tax ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"his campaign has been careful to avoid being drawn into a comparison on the point .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"And in reaction to Fehrnstrom 's comments Monday the campaign focused on whether the national health care law is constitutional .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"`` The Supreme Court left President Obama with two choices :","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"the federal individual mandate in Obamacare is either a constitutional tax or an unconstitutional penalty .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Governor Romney thinks","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"it is an unconstitutional penalty .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"What is President Obama 's position :","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"is his federal mandate unconstitutional","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"or is it a tax ? ''","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Romney campaign spokewsoman Amanda Henneberg said .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Rick Santorum , one of Romney 's former rivals for the GOP presidential nomination , said Thursday on CNN 's `` Piers Morgan Tonight ''","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that both Romney 's and Obama 's laws include an individual mandate tax .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"`` They have a series of problems with people","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"who decide to take the tax ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"in other words , pay the fine ,","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"instead of buying insurance ,","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"because it 's actually cheaper , particularly younger and healthier people","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"who - who are dropping out of the health care system , ''","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"he said of the Massachusetts case .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Santorum and other Republicans have been critical of the Massachusetts law ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"which Romney has defended as a state solution","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"which was valid under the state 's constitution ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"but not an appropriate national fix","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"to expanding insurance coverage .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"The matter of whether or not the national individual mandate is a tax has implications beyond what language is used in an election year .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"including Rep. Phil Gingrey of Georgia ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"argue","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"that the ruling makes their effort","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"to repeal the law easier","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"because tax laws are not subject to filibuster in the Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"which requires 60 votes","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"to overcome .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"The Senate can `` do it by reconciliation","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"since it 's a tax issue now ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"as Justice Roberts has redefined the law , ''","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Price said on CNN 's `` Starting Point '' Friday morning .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"On Sunday morning , Obama 's White House chief of staff explained the subtle distinction","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"Democrats used","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"to argue","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"the law was not a tax .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"`` Well , actually , they did n't call it a tax , ''","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Jack Lew said on CNN 's `` State of the Union . '' `` They said","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"it was using a power under the Constitution","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"that permits it .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"It was not labeled .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"`` And this is a penalty .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"It 's something","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"that only one percent of the people","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"who could afford insurance","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"who choose not to get it","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"will pay , ''","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"Lew continued .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Stephanie Cutter , Obama 's deputy campaign manager , said Friday on CNN 's Starting Point","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"argued","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"it was not a tax , but a penalty ,","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"`` if you choose not to get health care","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"and you 're imposing a hidden tax on all of us","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"because we pay for your health care ,","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"then you pay a penalty . ''","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"While campaigning in 2008 ,","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"Obama said","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"the health law would not result in a tax increase .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"`` If you are a family","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"making less than $ 250,000 a year ,","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"you will not see your taxes go up , ''","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"Obama said .","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"The Supreme Court found","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"that , `` the federal government does not have the power","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"to order people to buy health insurance . ''","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"`` The federal government does have the power","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"to impose a tax on those","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"without health insurance , ''","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"Chief Justice John Roberts wrote in the majority opinion .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"- CNN Political Producer Shawna Shepherd contributed to this report","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":275,"left